{
  "body": {
    "id": "pinterest01",
    "rows": [
      {
        "id": "header01",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "headercol",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "image",
                "id": "logoimg",
                "values": {
                  "src": {
                    "url": "https://cameronestateinn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Cameron-Estate-Logo.png",
                    "width": 180,
                    "height": 60,
                    "maxWidth": "50%",
                    "autoWidth": false
                  },
                  "alt": "Cameron Estate Inn",
                  "width": 200,
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "padding": "20px 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#2C3E50",
          "padding": "0 0 0 0"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "opening01",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "opencol01",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "heading",
                "id": "head01",
                "values": {
                  "text": "{{contact.first_name}},",
                  "tag": "h2",
                  "color": "#2C3E50",
                  "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                  "fontSize": 28,
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 10px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text01",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p>Quick question for you: What does your dream wedding actually look like?</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text02",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p>When you think about your wedding day — not what you're \"supposed to\" want, but what you actually envision — what do you see?</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#FDFCFA",
          "padding": "40px 40px 20px 40px"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "visions01",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "viscol01",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text03",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p><strong>Soft and romantic</strong> with lots of candlelight, fresh flowers everywhere, an intimate gathering of your closest people?</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text04",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p><strong>Bold and dramatic</strong> with rich, moody colors, a dramatic black-tie affair, making a statement with every detail?</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text05",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p><strong>Classic elegance</strong> — timeless, sophisticated, the kind of wedding that could have been in any era and still looks perfect?</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text06",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p><strong>A boho garden party</strong> — relaxed, organic, nature-inspired, completely you?</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text07",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p><strong>Something totally unexpected</strong> that perfectly captures you two as a couple, whatever that looks like?</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 20px 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#FFFFFF",
          "padding": "30px 40px 30px 40px"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "pinterest01",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "pintcol01",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "heading",
                "id": "head02",
                "values": {
                  "text": "That's Why We Created a Pinterest Board for You",
                  "tag": "h2",
                  "color": "#D4AF37",
                  "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                  "fontSize": 24,
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text08",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p>Grab a coffee, open Pinterest, and spend a few minutes scrolling through. See what makes you say \"oh, <strong>that's</strong> us.\" That's the fun part of wedding planning.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 25px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "button",
                "id": "btn01",
                "values": {
                  "text": "Browse Our Pinterest Board →",
                  "href": "https://pin.it/your-pinterest-board",
                  "backgroundColor": "#D4AF37",
                  "color": "#FFFFFF",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 0 0",
                  "borderRadius": 4
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#F5F1EB",
          "padding": "30px 40px 30px 40px"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "closing01",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "closecol01",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text09",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p>When you're ready to see how Cameron Estate can bring your Pinterest vision to life, I'd love to show you around.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "button",
                "id": "btn02",
                "values": {
                  "text": "Schedule Your Private Tour",
                  "href": "{{links.book_tour}}",
                  "backgroundColor": "#D4AF37",
                  "color": "#FFFFFF",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 0 0",
                  "borderRadius": 4
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "sig01",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p style=\"font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 500; color: #2C3E50;\">Talk soon,<br/>Lisa</p>",
                  "color": "#2C3E50",
                  "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                  "fontSize": 22,
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "30px 0 0 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#FDFCFA",
          "padding": "40px 40px 20px 40px"
        }
